metadata.name: Breathing Magic
metadata.description:
By Sneha Chakraborty | 1 July 2022

I am everything i have touched and seen. When I hurt you, I hurt myself, When I kissed you, I kissed myself. The vines and the stars, the moon and the butterflies all intertwine deep within my being.

I am merely person, yet here I am, painting a whole universe like never before.

Breathing Magic | Lbc_Sneha
